data.description: Turn key Short Term Rental opportunity or gorgeous primary home with 2 car garage on almost one half acre landscaped lot on least driven cul de sac at end of spacious gated community of Formosa Gardens Estates. So private that this and the surrounding large homes on oversized lots feel like mini estates of their own. Walking on to the welcoming front porch you will enter into a large bright foyer that opens to large formal living and dining rooms which open through double French doors to the incredible pool area with an enormous sunny pool deck and oversized sparkling pool.Next to the dining room the large open plan kitchen has a stainless steel refrigerator, dishwasher, gas stove and microwave. Opening to the large family room family guests can be entertained as the family chef prepares a gourmet meal surrounded by a kitchen table nook , food preparatory island and a large breakfast bar. This area is flooded by light through the windows and French doors opening to the covered lanai and screened in outside entertainment deck area with large heated pool and hot tub. Also opening to the pool area is the massive master bedroom suite wing with his and hers walk-in closets, high volume bathroom ceilings and windows which allow in beautiful morning light over his and hers vanities, garden tub and walk-in shower, and a private sitting room within its own access to the covered lanai and open pool deck area. There are also three other bedrooms and two full bathrooms on the first floor. Going up the stairs opens to a large area which can be used for multiple uses such as a movie theater,  office or games room but is now set up as a spacious second master suite almost apartment like with room for a king size bed and a full living area and full bathroom. The garage now can hold two cars with an additional space for lawn equipment and workshop, air conditioned when desired allowing for easy conversion into a theater or games room. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle relaxing in the resort like pool and spa or venture into the large yard to enjoy the Florida wildlife and tropical plants. Then travel less than one half block to enjoy catch and release bass fishing in either Star Lake or Moon Lake. Or use as a short term rental business such as AirB&B for the multitude of families that would love to stay in a gated, family friendly resort with The Formosa Winery open for enjoying wine and meals just outside the gates of our community, Margaritaville Resort with luxury hotel, expansive water park, entertainment venues, restaurants, clubs and shopping less than a mile away with special events and street entertainment open to the public almost daily, not to mention Walt Disney World Three miles away. Then drive on to Sea World, Universal Studios, the massive Orange County Convention Center, Amway Center, Camping World Stadium and Exploria Stadium for professional sports and world class entertainment, the city of Orlando with museums, Dr. Phillips Performig Art Center and clubs and restaurants, Icon Park with the Wheel and other attractions, shopping at Milennium Mall, Florida Mall and Prime Outlets, Plus I-4 linking some of the best beaches in Florida on both the Atlantic and Gulf of Mexico coasts less tha 80 miles away. Sounds like Paradise. You may never want to leave.
